Module com.github.sormuras.bach
Package com.github.sormuras.bach.lookup

Interface ModuleLookup

All Known Implementing Classes:
ExternalModuleLookup, GitHubReleasesModuleLookup, JavaFXModuleLookup, JUnit, JUnitJupiterModuleLookup, JUnitPlatformModuleLookup, LWJGLModuleLookup, SormurasModulesModuleLookup
Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface public interface ModuleLookup
A function that returns an optional string representation of a URI for a given module name.

See ExternalModuleLookup for an implementation that maps a single module name to a URI in a stable manner. See JUnitModuleLookup for an implementation that maps a set of module names to URIs that are related to a specific JUnit version.

See Also:
ExternalModuleLookup, JUnitModuleLookup
